net.zethmayr.benjamin.spring.common.mapper.base

Class ClassFieldMapper<C>

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.zethmayr.benjamin.spring.common.mapper.base.ClassFieldMapper<C>
  • Type Parameters:
    C - the object type of which this maps a field
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Mapper

    public abstract class ClassFieldMapper<C>
extends Object
    A mapper for any specific field of a given class.

    This acts as a loosely typed interface of Mapper. The sole concrete implementation is ComposedMapper.

    See Also:
    ComposedMapper
